description: Amendments to 06/00634/LTGDC for 178 new homes and 946m2 of commercial space (A1, A2, A3, B1, D1 D2). Propose the omission of 15 no. studio flats to be replaced with 10 no. 1 bed flats, resulting in a reduction in the total number of res. units to 173; reduction of car parking spaces, and other minor amendments. Additional amended plans received on 25/08/2009 proposing to amend the end residential unit of the proposed Rick Roberts Way terrace from a 3 storey 4-bed unit to a 2 storey 3-bed unit.
